wiki.summary: On “500lbs,” Lil Tecca flaunts the benefits of his position alongside noting his devotion for his significant other. The track was first previewed on June 2, 2023 through Taz Taylor’s Instagram story. The track later made an official release on July 21, 2023, followed by a Jordie Sanchez-directed music video a week later. Read more on Last.fm.
